20825618/hootie-the-blowfish-runite-tour-chicago-darius-rucker |title= Seems Like Old Times for Newly Reunited Hootie & the Blowfish |last=Despres |first=Tricia |work=[[Chicago Sun-Times]] |date=August 22, 2019 |accessdate=August 22, 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"cos\">{{Cite web |publisher=[[Consequence of Sound]] |last=Clark |first=Tyler |title=Hootie & the Blowfish Return with the Painfully Bland ''Imperfect Circle'' |date=October 30, 2019 |url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2019/10/album-review-hootie-and-the-blowfish-imperfect-circle/ |accessdate=November 2, 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"bbtl\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8529158/hootie-the-blowfish-imperfect-circle |title=Hootie & the Blowfish Reveals ''Imperfect Circle'' Track List, Shares 'Rollin'' |last=Graff |first=Gary |date=September 5, 2019 |accessdate=September 5, 2019 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"bbcountry\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8543338/miranda-lambert-wildcard-no-1-top-country-albums |title=Miranda Lambert Ties No.&nbsp;1 Record on Top Country Albums Chart, Hootie & the Blowfish Debut |last=Asker |first=Jim |date=November 12, 2019 |accessdate=November 12, 2019 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"bb\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8527067/hootie-the-blowfish-announce-imperfect-circle-album |title=Hootie & the Blowfish Announce ''Imperfect Circle', First Album in 15 Years |last=Aniftos |first=Rania |date=August 9, 2019 |accessdate=August 9, 2019 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"aria\">{{cite web|url=http://cdn.aria.com.au/pdfs/40F1405AA5D7C0456D4FBE2C2E70EFDBED1B410567EF5E5737D6A31C16B5643D/ARIA%20Digital%20Albums%20Chart.pdf?seq=26|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Digital Albums|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=November 11, 2019|accessdate=November 9, 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ap\">{{Cite web |url